        "timestamp": "2021-08-12 17:01:43.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 2:\n\nThis looks good Kevin, I think it is OK to leave the review open and wait for Jim to take a look.\n\nNow that you proved that these changes can coexist with the jpa changes in api/pap as Ram indicated, I think we need to determine an strategy forward to do it.   A few things to consider:\n\n- backup/restore strategy, should there be some form of it.\n\n- moving forward, how to ensure that developers working in models don't forget to modify the sql tables as necessary.\n\n- should clamp db tables be included ?\n\n- plan for oom integration.\n\nYou can take a look at the job that does db configuration:\n\nhttps://git.onap.org/oom/tree/kubernetes/policy/templates/job.yaml.\n\nWe would need db-migrator to run and integrate from this or a new job.\n\nOther thoughts?",
        "patchset_number": 2
      },
